        "message": "It's 6 AM for David in Fairview, TN (America/Chicago). Do the following:\n1. Check the cron job list (cron tool, action=list) and identify:\n   a. Any one-time (kind='at') reminders firing TODAY (between midnight and 11:59 PM Central)\n   b. Any one-time (kind='at') reminders firing TOMORROW\n   c. Any recurring jobs that are due to fire today or tomorrow (check nextRunAtMs)\n   Exclude the weather job and this briefing job from the list.\n2. Fetch weather from https://wttr.in/Fairview,TN?format=j1 for current conditions and moon data (moon_phase, moon_illumination, moonrise, moonset).\n3. Calculate the lunar day (day in the ~29.53-day cycle). Use known new moon Jan 29, 2025 as reference.\n4. Calculate the moon's approximate zodiac constellation using its ecliptic longitude (simplified algorithm: L = (218.316 + 13.176396*d) % 360, M_moon = (134.963 + 13.064993*d) % 360, lon = L + 6.289*sin(M_moon_radians), where d = days since J2000.0 = JD - 2451545.0).\n5. Send David a friendly morning briefing via Telegram (target=8697062578, channel=telegram) that includes:\n   - Good morning greeting with today's date\n   - Weather summary\n   - Moon section: phase name + emoji, lunar day (e.g. 'Day 12 of 29'), illumination %, constellation\n   - TODAY section: all reminders/events scheduled for today (if none, say so)\n   - TOMORROW section: all reminders/events scheduled for tomorrow (if none, say so)\nKeep it concise and friendly. David is in US Central Time."
      },
